title: Arnette Welcomes Chippa Wilson
description:
We are very proud to announce that Aussie aerial assassin Christopher "Chippa" Wilson is the newest member of our surf team family!

"I'm super stoked to join a rad company like Arnette because it's run by a cool group of people, the shades are great, and some of my favorite surfers are on the team," says Chippa.

We hope you enjoy Chippa's "Welcome to the Team" video featuring a track by Del.

Get the full story at: http://www.arnette.com/blog/arnette-w...

http://www.arnette.com
